#, no-wrap
msgid "By now, you should have a much better idea of what PAM can do, and how to make changes when needed. However, we must reiterate the importance of being very, *very* careful with any changes you make to PAM modules. You could lock yourself out of your system, or worse, let everyone else in.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/security/pam.md:351
